mysubs version 0.11
===================

mysubs is a lexically-scoped pragma that implements lexical subroutines i.e. subroutines whose definition
is restricted to the lexical scope in which they are visible.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Scope::Guard
  Devel::Hints::Lexical

